The SoC module has a label stating the model is "XHA5350" and a MAC label with a 00:0A:EB OUI.
In JW0008 can be found another module (brown PCB). UART is on unpopulated pins 39 - RX, 40 - TX
"PJW0002MAINXX1A", "JW0002-MAIN-2A", "WANSCAM", "120920" is silkscreened on the daughterboard. [[File:XHA5350_1.jpg|100px|thumbnail|left]][[File:XHA5350_2.jpg|100px|thumbnail|left]] [[File:jw0008_v2_front.jpg|100px|thumbnail|left]][[File:jw0008_v2_back.jpg|100px|thumbnail|left]]
